pr_title: Add option to toggle thank you redirect outside the webview
pr_body:
- Added `setThankyouRedirect` method to `SsSurvey` class to provide the option to toggle thank you page redirect outside the web-view after the survey is submitted.
- Updated README.md with the necessary instructions to use the `setThankyouRedirect` method.

pr_title: Fix issue - Unable to instantiate fragment - public constructor
pr_body:
This PR includes 

- Fix for the below issue
  ```
  androidx.fragment.app.Fragment$InstantiationException: Unable to instantiate fragment
  com.surveysparrow.ss_android_sdk.SsSurveyFragment: could not find Fragment constructor
  ```
- Updated Readme and SDK version in the examples to the latest.
